      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FASCINATE GLORY (4) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing eighth (31.46) in a Grade 5 at this track. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to her credit. Can atone. MISS GRAHAM (1) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at this track over 400m behind Songar Pearl (23.72) in a Grade 5. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Has ability and can atone. LILLY MOIRA (2) has missed the frame at her last two but did run well three back when second (23.61) in a Grade 5 at this track. With a good start should be able to take advantage of the low draw. Well placed here and can atone this time. BANJO'S FERNANDO (3) cannot be underestimated.",
